{"tid":2416531,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛科學debug: 疫苗統計學","createTime":"2021-02-21T06:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T08:55:01.000Z","uid":93141,"like":24,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8593750f64e925d6079194b40a821bd6f216d0fe","tid":2416531,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以解釋返一枝疫苗點解有效率可以負166%<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2415996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2415996</a><br />\n<br />\n本五毛入面見到好多cctoy連登仔唔識統計就發曬癲，決定輕輕出個post debug<br />\n<br />\n我會基於<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7745181/pdf/NEJMoa2034577.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7745181%2Fpdf%2FNEJMoa2034577.pdf&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=f5a080c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7745181/pdf/NEJMoa2034577.pdf</a><br />\n同 <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK431098/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK431098%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=09bbb98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK431098/</a><br />\n兩篇paper做解答<br />\n<br />\nQ1<br />\n事頭婆 ：有效率係唔會負數<br />\n有效率 = 成功接種人數/注射人數<br />\n點會有負數呀<br />\n<br />\nA1<br />\nvaccine efficacy並唔係單純既efficiency<br />\nefficiency既話咁講係冇錯，但科學實驗永遠都要有對照組 (control)<br />\n我永遠都可以冇啦啦搵到打完生理鹽水既人突然間冇事，但好有可能係心理作用/偶然，你唔會希望靠生理鹽水醫肺炎架嘛係咪<br />\n你要對照睇埋打安慰劑既人，同佢地比先知藥/疫苗係咪真係有用<br />\n所以effcacy條式簡單黎講其實係:<br />\n1-接種移民後有病人數/接種安慰劑後有病人數<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/csels/dsepd/ss1978/lesson3/section6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcsels%2Fdsepd%2Fss1978%2Flesson3%2Fsection6.html&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=416adaa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/csels/dsepd/ss1978/lesson3/section6.html</a><br />\n<br />\nQ2<br />\n紅豆默:<br />\n點解null hypothesis係揀冇效而唔係有效? 直接證明佢有效咪放心，搞一大輪野去證明唔到佢無效，即係有效/無效但係你證明失敗 係咪身有屎<br />\n<br />\nA2<br />\nnull hypothesis一直都係當冇用，因為occam&rsquo;s razor，你唔可以假設係有用，如果唔係我乜都claim有用咪唔駛test<br />\n我當然可以話假設宇宙某處有飛天意粉神，而你冇辦法reject我，因為你冇辦法行遍成個宇宙黎睇有冇飛天意粉神。但你會覺得我on99<br />\n例子已經咁可笑，到到用落人既疫苗更加唔可以假定有效，因為就會變左&ldquo;如果你證明唔到冇效，我就會打落你身上&rdquo;。咁你當然係要假定冇效，而去搵辦法證明有效。<br />\n簡單黎講，you should treat a hypothesis as a suspect, who remains innocent until proven guilty.<br />\n統計黎講，you can never accept a hypothesis，you can only reject a false hypothesis<br />\n<br />\nQ3<br />\n人面秀心:<br />\n有冇人可以解釋返一枝疫苗點解效率可以負<br />\n<br />\nA3<br />\n實際上表中efficacy本身並唔係負，負既係confidence interval<br />\n95% confidence interval既意思係，如果我地重複好多次同樣實驗(lets say 100次)，就會有95次實驗既efficacy落入呢個區域<br />\n因為係用odd ratio，好大機會係用<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK431098/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK431098%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=09bbb98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK431098/</a> 文中條式去計\bupper/lower bound<br />\n所以如果sample太細而且太偏，好有機會出現一變大一變細，甚至負既情況<br />\n<br />\nQ4<br />\n幫人面秀心補充:<br />\n咁efficacy有冇可能負<br />\n<br />\nA4<br />\n我地可以見到當發病人數sample太少<br />\n好有可能出現安慰劑發病人數反而少過疫苗發病人數既情況(不管疫苗有冇效)<br />\n睇返上面條式，呢個情況發生時，efficacy就會變負數<br />\n<br />\nQ5<br />\n幫大家補充:<br />\nconfidence interval出現負係咪代表支疫苗一定冇用<br />\n<br />\nA5<br />\n未必，我地應該話疫苗響呢個group未被證實有用<br />\n同樣情況響<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7745181/pdf/NEJMoa2034577.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7745181%2Fpdf%2FNEJMoa2034577.pdf&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=f5a080c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7745181/pdf/NEJMoa2034577.pdf</a> 一文中既&gt;75歲age group都有出現<br />\n原因就係sample size太細，就算efficacy係100%，個confidence interval都係大到不得了<br />\n但睇返所有人既話個efficacy同confidence interval反而就好正常<br />\n呢個情況可以參考Simpson&rsquo;s Paradox<br />\n當細group既efficacy同sample size差異好大時，就會出現大group有分別，細group冇分別既情況 (or vice versa)<br />\n<br />\n最後寄語連登仔，唔識唔緊要，可以查，可以問其他人，唔好做一股熱血但冇內涵既吳卓羲"},{"pid":"c70918b48a252b4e6760957d9b74d0dc7a238f67","tid":2416531,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"樓主心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b393ac9b498d10de2a899ec527a3554ed7e994a2","tid":2416531,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:45:55.000Z","msg":"樓主住響象牙塔幫港共維穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9575d094f05f33c6152c2d8256d22c1ddf9848","tid":2416531,"uid":372525,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:47:37.000Z","msg":"幫推，好多人唔識basic stat<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20db3600f3ee8f1174b5ee64b9c2fe5edd11586","tid":2416531,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b515b09190a818f70bd5b1cc77ca2c3236ff5f5a","tid":2416531,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"2d9575d094f05f33c6152c2d8256d22c1ddf9848","tid":2416531,"uid":372525,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:47:37.000Z","msg":"幫推，好多人唔識basic stat<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:49:13.000Z","msg":"能夠激到我重出江湖都係cctoy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaf566d50551af94d25f64755e63a1bc1f6189a","tid":2416531,"uid":93141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c70918b48a252b4e6760957d9b74d0dc7a23